00:56:18,458 --> 00:56:20,552
- I don't know what you want.
- Well, I don't.

759
00:56:21,879 --> 00:56:24,382
Which is why you gotta know
about the kid.

760
00:56:25,299 --> 00:56:27,552
What about the kid?

761
