[GROANS]

762
00:56:54,036 --> 00:56:55,333
[GROANS]

763
00:57:01,710 --> 00:57:03,804
DANNY: What's going on?
- Nothing.

764
00:57:06,089 --> 00:57:07,136
Just a scrape.

765
00:57:07,716 --> 00:57:09,138
It's fine, honey.

766
00:57:09,301 --> 00:57:10,928
It's just a scratch, okay?

767
00:57:11,094 --> 00:57:12,846
- You okay?
- Go back to bed. It's okay.

768
00:57:13,013 --> 00:57:14,230
Go back to bed.

769
00:57:14,389 --> 00:57:17,393
I just need to lay down
for a minute, okay?

770
00:57:18,310 --> 00:57:20,028
[MARY PANTING]

771
00:57:20,187 --> 00:57:22,940
Mary. What you need?
Can I get you something?

772
00:57:23,148 --> 00:57:25,822
Oh, uhn... I just need to lay down
and close my eyes...

773
00:57:25,984 --> 00:57:28,487
...for a couple of minutes, baby.
That's all.

774
00:57:30,072 --> 00:57:31,540
[SIGHS]

775
00:57:32,032 --> 00:57:34,455
When you're better, we'll go, right?

776
00:57:35,160 --> 00:57:36,457
We'll get out of here?

777
00:57:38,538 --> 00:57:40,757
Go somewhere far away, like you said?

778
00:57:42,584 --> 00:57:44,586
[LAUGHING]

779
00:57:46,755 --> 00:57:48,132
Tom was right.

780
00:57:49,925 --> 00:57:51,723
He ain't never gonna let me go.

781
00:57:53,261 --> 00:57:56,105
- I tried.
- Well, try again. That's bullshit, Mary.

782
00:58:00,185 --> 00:58:01,232
[GROANS]

783
00:58:01,436 --> 00:58:02,858
I tried.

784
00:58:03,063 --> 00:58:05,065
[♪♪♪]

